com.ge.dspmicro.tcpsocketserver.api

Class TCPSocketMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ge.dspmicro.tcpsocketserver.api.TCPSocketMessage
  • Deprecated. 
    Use java.nio.channels.ServerSocketChannel to manage socket connections.

    @Deprecated
public class TCPSocketMessage
extends Object
    A structured format for sending messages over TCP sockets. It's up to the individual ITCPSocketService implementation to use the message components as part of a communication protocol.

    Message Format:
    - serviceID - integer identifying the server side service
    - extProgramName - String identifying the the external client
    - messageID - integer can be used for sequencing messages
    - commandCode - integer can be used to fork service actions on payload
    - payload - byte array payload
